    "In each state, the function block to test is called with the LLM-generated input variables, and then the expected outputs are checked in the next cycle.",
    "The ST-code also contains embedded C-code to later print out test monitoring data during test execution.",
    "We implemented a prototype of the Test Case Generator in Python, using LangChainfoot_0 for LLM interactions.",
    "GPT-4-0613 served as the LLM to query and was configured to stream the outputs to standard output so that the test case generation process could be monitored.",
